      "updated": 1766899295700,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": " Non Functional Req\n- low latency (url creation, on redirect ~200ms)\n- Scale: 100M DAU/1B url\n- shorten url should be unique\n- CAP: availability >> consistency (eventual)",
